---
title: Mexican Plant-Based Mince Quesadillas with Charred Corn Salsa & Plant-Based Cheese
description: In this cosy quesadilla dish, pack all of your plant-based favourites into golden and crispy tortillas for a meal packed with maximum flavour. No Mexican dish is complete without a salsa, so on the menu tonight, is a corn and tomato one.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64cc492be287ce21da88329b-5855e898.jpeg
